        <updateDate>2006-11-28T17:35:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[Gold Star Parents Annuity Act - Directs the Secretary of Defense to pay a special pension to each person who has received a Gold Star lapel pin as a parent of a member of the armed forces who died while serving.]]></text>
      </summary>
